# <%= projectName %>

## Prerequisites

- Nix for the generated language-specific development shell

## Setup

```bash
nix develop path:.
go mod tidy
pre-commit install
make check
```

The generated `flake.nix` provides Go <%= toolchain.go %>+ plus `golangci-lint`,
`staticcheck`, `deadcode`, `govulncheck`, `goimports`, `go-mutesting`,
`gitleaks`, and `pre-commit`.

## Development

| Command | Description |
| --- | --- |
| `make lint` | Run golangci-lint and custom anvil analyzers |
| `make test` | Run Go tests |
| `make check` | Run tier 1 and tier 2 validation |
| `make quality` | Run all validation, including mutation testing |
| `make fix` | Auto-format Go source files |

## Project Structure

```text
cmd/app/         Application entrypoint
internal/seed/   Reference package and tests
tools/           Tool tracking and custom analyzers
```
